@NODE SHAREWARE "If you like this program..."
@{b}If you like this little program...@{ub}
**********************************

you can fill out the registration-form and (e-)mail it to me. In connection
with DM 15,- cash or 10 US-$ cash (inside Germany: DM 10,-) I will send you
a postcard or e-mail with your personal registration data and code.

You only need to pay DM 10,- or US-$ 8 if you have an e-mail address!

Your registration data will be valid for all Funky 5.x versions.

You may also transfer the money to my german bank account (see below; don't
forget your name!).

If you want to use another payment method, please contact me. I do NOT take
any credit cards!!

Please give me some days for the delivery!

Contact:

                               Peter F. Gath
                             Gabaeckerweg 40/1
                             D-73630 Remshalden
                                  Germany
                          
                 E-Mail: Peter.Gath@studbox.uni-stuttgart.de

Bank account:

                        Kreissparkasse Remshalden
                        Bank Code Number 602 500 13
